<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>REES&#160;28914.  New Directions in Slavic Studies.  100 Units.</strong></p><p class="courseblockdesc">
This seminar examines the recent major works of scholarship in Slavic, East European, and Eurasian Studies, taking stock of the current state of the field. It introduces the interdisciplinary research methods (e.g. historical, anthropological, digital studies, etc.) that have driven new developments in SEES.</p><p class="courseblockdetail">
